mysql_groundtruth: SELECT PLAYER_ID, DEVICE_ID FROM ACTIVITY WHERE (PLAYER_ID, EVENT_DATE) IN ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, MIN(EVENT_DATE) FROM ACTIVITY GROUP BY PLAYER_ID )

SELECT A1.PLAYER_ID, A1.DEVICE_ID FROM ACTIVITY A1 JOIN ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, MIN(EVENT_DATE) AS FIRST_LOGIN FROM ACTIVITY GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) A2 ON ( A1.PLAYER_ID=A2.PLAYER_ID AND A1.EVENT_DATE=A2.FIRST_LOGIN )
